#. <section class="sutta" id="mn14"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "mn14:0.1"
msgid "Majjhima Nikāya 14"
msgstr "Middle Discourses 14"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "mn14:0.2"
msgid "Cūḷadukkhakkhandhasutta"
msgstr "The Shorter Discourse on the Mass of Suffering"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya1"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.91"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "mn14:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sakkesu viharati kapilavatthusmiṃ nigrodhārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Sakyans, near "
"Kapilavatthu in the Banyan Tree Monastery."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya2"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho mahānāmo sakko yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho mahānāmo "
"sakko bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Mahānāma the Sakyan went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, "
"and said to him:"

msgctxt "mn14:2.2"
msgid "“dīgharattāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā evaṃ dhammaṃ desitaṃ ājānāmi:"
msgstr "“For a long time, sir, I have understood your teaching like this:"

#. VAR: ‘lobho cittassa upakkileso, doso cittassa upakkileso, moho cittassa upakkileso’ti → idaṃ vākyaṃ syā1 potthake
msgctxt "mn14:2.3"
msgid ""
"‘lobho cittassa upakkileso, doso cittassa upakkileso, moho cittassa "
"upakkileso’ti."
msgstr "‘Greed, hate, and delusion are corruptions of the mind.’"

#. VAR: Evañcāhaṃ → evaṃpāhaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "mn14:2.4"
msgid "Evañcāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā dhammaṃ desitaṃ ājānāmi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn14:2.5"
msgid ""
"‘lobho cittassa upakkileso, doso cittassa upakkileso, moho cittassa "
"upakkileso’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn14:2.6"
msgid ""
"Atha ca pana me ekadā lobhadhammāpi cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhanti, "
"dosadhammāpi cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhanti, mohadhammāpi cittaṃ pariyādāya "
"tiṭṭhanti."
msgstr ""
"Despite understanding this, sometimes my mind is occupied by thoughts of "
"greed, hate, and delusion."

msgctxt "mn14:2.7"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn14:2.8"
msgid ""
"‘kosu nāma me dhammo ajjhattaṃ appahīno yena me ekadā lobhadhammāpi cittaṃ "
"pariyādāya tiṭṭhanti, dosadhammāpi cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhanti, mohadhammāpi "
"cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhantī’”ti."
msgstr "I wonder what qualities remain in me that I have such thoughts?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya3"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:3.1"
msgid ""
"“So eva kho te, mahānāma, dhammo ajjhattaṃ appahīno yena te ekadā "
"lobhadhammāpi cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhanti, dosadhammāpi cittaṃ pariyādāya "
"tiṭṭhanti, mohadhammāpi cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhanti."
msgstr ""
"“Mahānāma, there is a quality that remains in you that makes you have such "
"thoughts."

msgctxt "mn14:3.2"
msgid ""
"So ca hi te, mahānāma, dhammo ajjhattaṃ pahīno abhavissa, na tvaṃ agāraṃ "
"ajjhāvaseyyāsi, na kāme paribhuñjeyyāsi."
msgstr ""
"For if you had given up that quality you would not still be living at home "
"and enjoying sensual pleasures."

msgctxt "mn14:3.3"
msgid ""
"Yasmā ca kho te, mahānāma, so eva dhammo ajjhattaṃ appahīno tasmā tvaṃ "
"agāraṃ ajjhāvasasi, kāme paribhuñjasi."
msgstr ""
"But because you haven’t given up that quality you are still living at home "
"and enjoying sensual pleasures."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya4"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: bahupāyāsā → bahūpāyāsā (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "mn14:4.1"
msgid "‘Appassādā kāmā bahudukkhā bahupāyāsā, ādīnavo ettha bhiyyo’ti—"
msgstr ""
"Sensual pleasures give little gratification and much suffering and distress, "
"and they are all the more full of drawbacks."

#. VAR: hoti, so ca → sova (mr)
msgctxt "mn14:4.2"
msgid ""
"iti cepi, mahānāma, ariyasāvakassa yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhaṃ hoti, "
"so ca aññatreva kāmehi aññatra akusalehi dhammehi pītisukhaṃ nādhigacchati, "
"aññaṃ vā tato santataraṃ;"
msgstr ""
"Even though a noble disciple has clearly seen this with right wisdom, so "
"long as they don’t achieve the rapture and bliss that are apart from sensual "
"pleasures and unskillful qualities, or something even more peaceful than "
"that,"

msgctxt "mn14:4.3"
msgid "atha kho so neva tāva anāvaṭṭī kāmesu hoti."
msgstr "they might still return to sensual pleasures."

msgctxt "mn14:4.4"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho, mahānāma, ariyasāvakassa ‘appassādā kāmā bahudukkhā bahupāyāsā, "
"ādīnavo ettha bhiyyo’ti—evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhaṃ hoti, "
"so ca aññatreva kāmehi aññatra akusalehi dhammehi pītisukhaṃ adhigacchati "
"aññaṃ vā tato santataraṃ;"
msgstr ""
"But when they do achieve that rapture and bliss, or something more peaceful "
"than that,"

msgctxt "mn14:4.5"
msgid "atha kho so anāvaṭṭī kāmesu hoti."
msgstr "they will not return to sensual pleasures."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya5"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.92"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:5.1"
msgid ""
"Mayhampi kho, mahānāma, pubbeva sambodhā, anabhisambuddhassa bodhisattasseva "
"sato, "
msgstr ""
"Before my awakening—when I was still unawakened but intent on awakening—I "
"too clearly saw with right wisdom that: "

msgctxt "mn14:5.2"
msgid ""
"‘appassādā kāmā bahudukkhā bahupāyāsā, ādīnavo ettha bhiyyo’ti—evametaṃ "
"yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhaṃ hoti,"
msgstr ""
"‘Sensual pleasures give little gratification and much suffering and "
"distress, and they are all the more full of drawbacks.’"

#. VAR: ca → sova (mr)
msgctxt "mn14:5.3"
msgid ""
"so ca aññatreva kāmehi aññatra akusalehi dhammehi pītisukhaṃ nājjhagamaṃ, "
"aññaṃ vā tato santataraṃ;"
msgstr ""
"But so long as I didn’t achieve the rapture and bliss that are apart from "
"sensual pleasures and unskillful qualities, or something even more peaceful "
"than that,"

msgctxt "mn14:5.4"
msgid "atha khvāhaṃ neva tāva anāvaṭṭī kāmesu paccaññāsiṃ."
msgstr "I didn’t announce that I would not return to sensual pleasures."

msgctxt "mn14:5.5"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho me, mahānāma, ‘appassādā kāmā bahudukkhā bahupāyāsā, ādīnavo "
"ettha bhiyyo’ti—evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhaṃ ahosi, so ca "
"aññatreva kāmehi aññatra akusalehi dhammehi pītisukhaṃ ajjhagamaṃ, aññaṃ vā "
"tato santataraṃ;"
msgstr ""
"But when I did achieve that rapture and bliss, or something more peaceful "
"than that,"

msgctxt "mn14:5.6"
msgid "athāhaṃ anāvaṭṭī kāmesu paccaññāsiṃ."
msgstr "I announced that I would not return to sensual pleasures."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya6"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:6.1"
msgid "Ko ca, mahānāma, kāmānaṃ assādo?"
msgstr "And what is the gratification of sensual pleasures?"

msgctxt "mn14:6.2"
msgid "Pañcime, mahānāma, kāmaguṇā."
msgstr "There are these five kinds of sensual stimulation."

msgctxt "mn14:6.3"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "mn14:6.4"
msgid "Cakkhuviññeyyā rūpā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā piyarūpā kāmūpasaṃhitā rajanīyā;"
msgstr ""
"Sights known by the eye that are likable, desirable, agreeable, pleasant, "
"sensual, and arousing."

msgctxt "mn14:6.5"
msgid "sotaviññeyyā saddā … pe …"
msgstr "Sounds known by the ear …"

msgctxt "mn14:6.6"
msgid "ghānaviññeyyā gandhā …"
msgstr "Smells known by the nose …"

msgctxt "mn14:6.7"
msgid "jivhāviññeyyā rasā …"
msgstr "Tastes known by the tongue …"

msgctxt "mn14:6.8"
msgid ""
"kāyaviññeyyā phoṭṭhabbā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā piyarūpā kāmūpasaṃhitā rajanīyā—"
msgstr ""
"Touches known by the body that are likable, desirable, agreeable, pleasant, "
"sensual, and arousing."

msgctxt "mn14:6.9"
msgid "ime kho, mahānāma, pañca kāmaguṇā."
msgstr "These are the five kinds of sensual stimulation."

msgctxt "mn14:6.10"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ kho, mahānāma, ime pañca kāmaguṇe paṭicca uppajjati sukhaṃ somanassaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"The pleasure and happiness that arise from these five kinds of sensual "
"stimulation: this is the gratification of sensual pleasures."

msgctxt "mn14:6.11"
msgid "ayaṃ kāmānaṃ assādo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya7"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:7.1"
msgid "Ko ca, mahānāma, kāmānaṃ ādīnavo?"
msgstr "And what is the drawback of sensual pleasures?"

msgctxt "mn14:7.2"
msgid "Idha, mahānāma, kulaputto yena sippaṭṭhānena jīvikaṃ kappeti—"
msgstr "It’s when a respectable person earns a living by means such as"

msgctxt "mn14:7.3"
msgid ""
"yadi muddāya yadi gaṇanāya yadi saṅkhānena yadi kasiyā yadi vaṇijjāya yadi "
"gorakkhena yadi issatthena yadi rājaporisena yadi sippaññatarena, "
msgstr ""
"computing, accounting, calculating, farming, trade, raising cattle, archery, "
"government service, or one of the professions. "

msgctxt "mn14:7.4"
msgid ""
"sītassa purakkhato uṇhassa purakkhato ḍaṃsamakasavātātapasarīsapasamphassehi "
"rissamāno khuppipāsāya mīyamāno;"
msgstr ""
"But they must face cold and heat, being hurt by the touch of flies, "
"mosquitoes, wind, sun, and reptiles, and risking death from hunger and "
"thirst."

msgctxt "mn14:7.5"
msgid ""
"ayampi, mahānāma, kāmānaṃ ādīnavo sandiṭṭhiko dukkhakkhandho kāmahetu "
"kāmanidānaṃ kāmādhikaraṇaṃ kāmānameva hetu."
msgstr ""
"This is a drawback of sensual pleasures apparent in this very life, a mass "
"of suffering caused by sensual pleasures."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya8"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:8.1"
msgid ""
"Tassa ce, mahānāma, kulaputtassa evaṃ uṭṭhahato ghaṭato vāyamato te bhogā "
"nābhinipphajjanti, "
msgstr ""
"That respectable person might try hard, strive, and make an effort, but fail "
"to earn any money. "

msgctxt "mn14:8.2"
msgid ""
"so socati kilamati paridevati urattāḷiṃ kandati sammohaṃ āpajjati ‘moghaṃ "
"vata me uṭṭhānaṃ, aphalo vata me vāyāmo’ti."
msgstr ""
"If this happens, they sorrow and pine and lament, beating their breast and "
"falling into confusion, saying: ‘Oh, my hard work is wasted. My efforts are "
"fruitless!’"

msgctxt "mn14:8.3"
msgid ""
"Ayampi, mahānāma, kāmānaṃ ādīnavo sandiṭṭhiko dukkhakkhandho kāmahetu "
"kāmanidānaṃ kāmādhikaraṇaṃ kāmānameva hetu."
msgstr ""
"This too is a drawback of sensual pleasures apparent in this very life, a "
"mass of suffering caused by sensual pleasures."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya9"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:9.1"
msgid ""
"Tassa ce, mahānāma, kulaputtassa evaṃ uṭṭhahato ghaṭato vāyamato te bhogā "
"abhinipphajjanti."
msgstr ""
"That respectable person might try hard, strive, and make an effort, and "
"succeed in earning money."

msgctxt "mn14:9.2"
msgid "So tesaṃ bhogānaṃ ārakkhādhikaraṇaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti:"
msgstr ""
"But they experience pain and sadness when they try to protect it, thinking:"

msgctxt "mn14:9.3"
msgid ""
"‘kinti me bhoge neva rājāno hareyyuṃ, na corā hareyyuṃ, na aggi daheyya, na "
"udakaṃ vaheyya, na appiyā vā dāyādā hareyyun’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘How can I prevent my wealth from being taken by rulers or bandits, consumed "
"by fire, swept away by flood, or taken by unloved heirs?’"

msgctxt "mn14:9.4"
msgid ""
"Tassa evaṃ ārakkhato gopayato te bhoge rājāno vā haranti, corā vā haranti, "
"aggi vā dahati, udakaṃ vā vahati, appiyā vā dāyādā haranti."
msgstr ""
"And even though they protect it and ward it, rulers or bandits take it, or "
"fire consumes it, or flood sweeps it away, or unloved heirs take it."

msgctxt "mn14:9.5"
msgid "So socati kilamati paridevati urattāḷiṃ kandati sammohaṃ āpajjati:"
msgstr ""
"They sorrow and pine and lament, beating their breast and falling into "
"confusion:"

msgctxt "mn14:9.6"
msgid "‘yampi me ahosi tampi no natthī’ti."
msgstr "‘What used to be mine is gone.’"

msgctxt "mn14:9.7"
msgid ""
"Ayampi, mahānāma, kāmānaṃ ādīnavo sandiṭṭhiko dukkhakkhandho kāmahetu "
"kāmanidānaṃ kāmādhikaraṇaṃ kāmānameva hetu."
msgstr ""
"This too is a drawback of sensual pleasures apparent in this very life, a "
"mass of suffering caused by sensual pleasures."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya10"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:10.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, mahānāma, kāmahetu kāmanidānaṃ kāmādhikaraṇaṃ kāmānameva hetu "
"rājānopi rājūhi vivadanti, khattiyāpi khattiyehi vivadanti, brāhmaṇāpi "
"brāhmaṇehi vivadanti, gahapatīpi gahapatīhi vivadanti, mātāpi puttena "
"vivadati, puttopi mātarā vivadati, pitāpi puttena vivadati, puttopi pitarā "
"vivadati, bhātāpi bhātarā vivadati, bhātāpi bhaginiyā vivadati, bhaginīpi "
"bhātarā vivadati, sahāyopi sahāyena vivadati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, for the sake of sensual pleasures kings fight with kings, "
"aristocrats fight with aristocrats, brahmins fight with brahmins, and "
"householders fight with householders. A mother fights with her child, child "
"with mother, father with child, and child with father. Brother fights with "
"brother, brother with sister, sister with brother, and friend fights with "
"friend."

msgctxt "mn14:10.2"
msgid ""
"Te tattha kalahaviggahavivādāpannā aññamaññaṃ pāṇīhipi upakkamanti, "
"leḍḍūhipi upakkamanti, daṇḍehipi upakkamanti, satthehipi upakkamanti."
msgstr ""
"Once they’ve started quarreling, arguing, and fighting, they attack each "
"other with fists, stones, rods, and swords,"

msgctxt "mn14:10.3"
msgid "Te tattha maraṇampi nigacchanti, maraṇamattampi dukkhaṃ."
msgstr "resulting in death and deadly pain."

msgctxt "mn14:10.4"
msgid ""
"Ayampi, mahānāma, kāmānaṃ ādīnavo sandiṭṭhiko dukkhakkhandho kāmahetu "
"kāmanidānaṃ kāmādhikaraṇaṃ kāmānameva hetu."
msgstr ""
"This too is a drawback of sensual pleasures apparent in this very life, a "
"mass of suffering caused by sensual pleasures."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:11.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, mahānāma, kāmahetu kāmanidānaṃ kāmādhikaraṇaṃ kāmānameva hetu "
"asicammaṃ gahetvā, dhanukalāpaṃ sannayhitvā, ubhatobyūḷhaṃ saṅgāmaṃ "
"pakkhandanti usūsupi khippamānesu, sattīsupi khippamānāsu, asīsupi "
"vijjotalantesu."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, for the sake of sensual pleasures they don their sword and "
"shield, fasten their bow and arrows, and plunge into a battle massed on both "
"sides, with arrows and spears flying and swords flashing."

msgctxt "mn14:11.2"
msgid ""
"Te tattha usūhipi vijjhanti, sattiyāpi vijjhanti, asināpi sīsaṃ chindanti."
msgstr ""
"There they are struck with arrows and spears, and their heads are chopped "
"off,"

msgctxt "mn14:11.3"
msgid "Te tattha maraṇampi nigacchanti, maraṇamattampi dukkhaṃ."
msgstr "resulting in death and deadly pain."

msgctxt "mn14:11.4"
msgid ""
"Ayampi, mahānāma, kāmānaṃ ādīnavo sandiṭṭhiko dukkhakkhandho kāmahetu "
"kāmanidānaṃ kāmādhikaraṇaṃ kāmānameva hetu."
msgstr ""
"This too is a drawback of sensual pleasures apparent in this very life, a "
"mass of suffering caused by sensual pleasures."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:12.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, mahānāma, kāmahetu kāmanidānaṃ kāmādhikaraṇaṃ kāmānameva hetu "
"asicammaṃ gahetvā, dhanukalāpaṃ sannayhitvā, addāvalepanā upakāriyo "
"pakkhandanti usūsupi khippamānesu, sattīsupi khippamānāsu, asīsupi "
"vijjotalantesu."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, for the sake of sensual pleasures they don their sword and "
"shield, fasten their bow and arrows, and charge wetly plastered bastions, "
"with arrows and spears flying and swords flashing."

msgctxt "mn14:12.2"
msgid ""
"Te tattha usūhipi vijjhanti, sattiyāpi vijjhanti, chakaṇakāyapi osiñcanti, "
"abhivaggenapi omaddanti, asināpi sīsaṃ chindanti."
msgstr ""
"There they are struck with arrows and spears, splashed with dung, crushed "
"with spiked blocks, and their heads are chopped off,"

msgctxt "mn14:12.3"
msgid "Te tattha maraṇampi nigacchanti, maraṇamattampi dukkhaṃ."
msgstr "resulting in death and deadly pain."

msgctxt "mn14:12.4"
msgid ""
"Ayampi, mahānāma, kāmānaṃ ādīnavo sandiṭṭhiko dukkhakkhandho kāmahetu "
"kāmanidānaṃ kāmādhikaraṇaṃ kāmānameva hetu."
msgstr ""
"This too is a drawback of sensual pleasures apparent in this very life, a "
"mass of suffering caused by sensual pleasures."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya13"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:13.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, mahānāma, kāmahetu kāmanidānaṃ kāmādhikaraṇaṃ kāmānameva hetu "
"sandhimpi chindanti, nillopampi haranti, ekāgārikampi karonti, paripanthepi "
"tiṭṭhanti, paradārampi gacchanti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, for the sake of sensual pleasures they break into houses, "
"plunder wealth, steal from isolated buildings, commit highway robbery, and "
"commit adultery."

msgctxt "mn14:13.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ rājāno gahetvā vividhā kammakāraṇā kārenti—"
msgstr "The rulers would arrest them and subject them to various punishments—"

msgctxt "mn14:13.3"
msgid ""
"kasāhipi tāḷenti, vettehipi tāḷenti, aḍḍhadaṇḍakehipi tāḷenti; hatthampi "
"chindanti, pādampi chindanti, hatthapādampi chindanti, kaṇṇampi chindanti, "
"nāsampi chindanti, kaṇṇanāsampi chindanti; bilaṅgathālikampi karonti, "
"saṅkhamuṇḍikampi karonti, rāhumukhampi karonti, jotimālikampi karonti, "
"hatthapajjotikampi karonti, erakavattikampi karonti, cīrakavāsikampi "
"karonti, eṇeyyakampi karonti, baḷisamaṃsikampi karonti, kahāpaṇikampi "
"karonti, khārāpatacchikampi karonti, palighaparivattikampi karonti, "
"palālapīṭhakampi karonti, tattenapi telena osiñcanti, sunakhehipi "
"khādāpenti, jīvantampi sūle uttāsenti, asināpi sīsaṃ chindanti."
msgstr ""
"whipping, caning, and clubbing; cutting off hands or feet, or both; cutting "
"off ears or nose, or both; the ‘porridge pot’, the ‘shell-shave’, the ‘demon’"
"s mouth’, the ‘garland of fire’, the ‘burning hand’, the ‘grass blades’, the "
"‘bark dress’, the ‘antelope’, the ‘meat hook’, the ‘coins’, the ‘acid pickle’"
", the ‘twisting bar’, the ‘straw mat’; being splashed with hot oil, being "
"fed to the dogs, being impaled alive, and being beheaded."

msgctxt "mn14:13.4"
msgid "Te tattha maraṇampi nigacchanti, maraṇamattampi dukkhaṃ."
msgstr "These result in death and deadly pain."

msgctxt "mn14:13.5"
msgid ""
"Ayampi, mahānāma, kāmānaṃ ādīnavo sandiṭṭhiko dukkhakkhandho kāmahetu "
"kāmanidānaṃ kāmādhikaraṇaṃ kāmānameva hetu."
msgstr ""
"This too is a drawback of sensual pleasures apparent in this very life, a "
"mass of suffering caused by sensual pleasures."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya14"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:14.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, mahānāma, kāmahetu kāmanidānaṃ kāmādhikaraṇaṃ kāmānameva hetu "
"kāyena duccaritaṃ caranti, vācāya duccaritaṃ caranti, manasā duccaritaṃ "
"caranti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, for the sake of sensual pleasures, they conduct themselves "
"badly by way of body, speech, and mind."

msgctxt "mn14:14.2"
msgid ""
"Te kāyena duccaritaṃ caritvā, vācāya duccaritaṃ caritvā, manasā duccaritaṃ "
"caritvā, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā, apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ "
"upapajjanti."
msgstr ""
"When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a place of loss, a "
"bad place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "mn14:14.3"
msgid ""
"Ayampi, mahānāma, kāmānaṃ ādīnavo samparāyiko, dukkhakkhandho kāmahetu "
"kāmanidānaṃ kāmādhikaraṇaṃ kāmānameva hetu."
msgstr ""
"This is a drawback of sensual pleasures to do with lives to come, a mass of "
"suffering caused by sensual pleasures."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya15"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.93"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:15.1"
msgid "Ekamidāhaṃ, mahānāma, samayaṃ rājagahe viharāmi gijjhakūṭe pabbate."
msgstr ""
"Mahānāma, this one time I was staying near Rājagaha, on the Vulture’s Peak "
"Mountain."

#. VAR: nigaṇṭhā → niganthā (s1-3, mr)
msgctxt "mn14:15.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena sambahulā nigaṇṭhā isigilipasse kāḷasilāyaṃ "
"ubbhaṭṭhakā honti āsanapaṭikkhittā, opakkamikā dukkhā tibbā kharā kaṭukā "
"vedanā vedayanti."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time several Jain ascetics on the slopes of Isigili at the Black "
"Rock were constantly standing, refusing seats. And they felt painful, sharp, "
"severe, acute feelings due to overexertion."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya16"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:16.1"
msgid ""
"Atha khvāhaṃ, mahānāma, sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yena "
"isigilipasse kāḷasilā yena te nigaṇṭhā tenupasaṅkamiṃ; upasaṅkamitvā te "
"nigaṇṭhe etadavocaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"Then in the late afternoon, I came out of retreat and went to the Black Rock "
"to visit those Jain ascetics. I said to them:"

msgctxt "mn14:16.2"
msgid ""
"‘kiṃ nu tumhe, āvuso nigaṇṭhā, ubbhaṭṭhakā āsanapaṭikkhittā, opakkamikā "
"dukkhā tibbā kharā kaṭukā vedanā vedayathā’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘Reverends, why are you constantly standing, refusing seats, so that you "
"feel painful, sharp, severe, acute feelings due to overexertion?’"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya17"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:17.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, mahānāma, te nigaṇṭhā maṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr "When I said this, those Jain ascetics said to me:"

#. VAR: nāṭaputto → nātaputto (bj) | nāthaputto (pts1)
msgctxt "mn14:17.2"
msgid ""
"‘nigaṇṭho, āvuso, nāṭaputto sabbaññū sabbadassāvī aparisesaṃ ñāṇadassanaṃ "
"paṭijānāti:"
msgstr ""
"‘Reverend, the Jain leader Nātaputta claims to be all-knowing and all-"
"seeing, to know and see everything without exception, thus:"

msgctxt "mn14:17.3"
msgid ""
"“carato ca me tiṭṭhato ca suttassa ca jāgarassa ca satataṃ samitaṃ "
"ñāṇadassanaṃ paccupaṭṭhitan”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Knowledge and vision are constantly and continually present to me, while "
"walking, standing, sleeping, and waking.”"

msgctxt "mn14:17.4"
msgid "So evamāha:"
msgstr "He says:"

#. VAR: atthi kho vo → atthi vo (bj) | atthi kho bho (s1-3, mr)
#. VAR: nijjīretha → nijjaretha (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "mn14:17.5"
msgid ""
"“atthi kho vo, nigaṇṭhā, pubbe pāpakammaṃ kataṃ, taṃ imāya kaṭukāya "
"dukkarakārikāya nijjīretha;"
msgstr ""
"“O Jain ascetics, you have done bad deeds in a past life. Wear them away "
"with these severe and grueling austerities."

#. VAR: yaṃ panettha → mayaṃ panettha (mr)
msgctxt "mn14:17.6"
msgid ""
"yaṃ panettha etarahi kāyena saṃvutā vācāya saṃvutā manasā saṃvutā taṃ āyatiṃ "
"pāpassa kammassa akaraṇaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"And when you refrain from such deeds in the present by way of body, speech, "
"and mind, you’re not doing any bad deeds for the future."

msgctxt "mn14:17.7"
msgid ""
"iti purāṇānaṃ kammānaṃ tapasā byantibhāvā, navānaṃ kammānaṃ akaraṇā, āyatiṃ "
"anavassavo;"
msgstr ""
"So, due to eliminating past deeds by mortification, and not doing any new "
"deeds, there’s nothing to come up in the future."

# https://discourse.suttacentral.net/t/the-future-perfect-tense-in-pali/4630/20
msgctxt "mn14:17.8"
msgid ""
"āyatiṃ anavassavā kammakkhayo, kammakkhayā dukkhakkhayo, dukkhakkhayā "
"vedanākkhayo, vedanākkhayā sabbaṃ dukkhaṃ nijjiṇṇaṃ bhavissatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"With nothing to come up in the future, deeds end. With the ending of deeds, "
"suffering ends. With the ending of suffering, feeling ends. And with the "
"ending of feeling, all suffering will have been worn away.”"

msgctxt "mn14:17.9"
msgid "Tañca panamhākaṃ ruccati ceva khamati ca, tena camha attamanā’ti."
msgstr "We approve and accept this, and we are satisfied with it.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya18"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:18.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, ahaṃ, mahānāma, te nigaṇṭhe etadavocaṃ:"
msgstr "When they said this, I said to them:"

msgctxt "mn14:18.2"
msgid "‘kiṃ pana tumhe, āvuso nigaṇṭhā, jānātha—"
msgstr "‘But reverends, do you know"

msgctxt "mn14:18.3"
msgid "ahuvamheva mayaṃ pubbe na nāhuvamhā’ti?"
msgstr ""
"for sure that you existed in the past, and it is not the case that you didn’"
"t exist?’"

msgctxt "mn14:18.4"
msgid "‘No hidaṃ, āvuso’."
msgstr "‘No we don’t, reverend.’"

msgctxt "mn14:18.5"
msgid "‘Kiṃ pana tumhe, āvuso nigaṇṭhā, jānātha—"
msgstr "‘But reverends, do you know"

msgctxt "mn14:18.6"
msgid "akaramheva mayaṃ pubbe pāpakammaṃ na nākaramhā’ti?"
msgstr "for sure that you did bad deeds in the past?’"

msgctxt "mn14:18.7"
msgid "‘No hidaṃ, āvuso’."
msgstr "‘No we don’t, reverend.’"

msgctxt "mn14:18.8"
msgid "‘Kiṃ pana tumhe, āvuso nigaṇṭhā, jānātha—"
msgstr "‘But reverends, do you know"

msgctxt "mn14:18.9"
msgid "evarūpaṃ vā evarūpaṃ vā pāpakammaṃ akaramhā’ti?"
msgstr "that you did such and such bad deeds?’"

msgctxt "mn14:18.10"
msgid "‘No hidaṃ, āvuso’."
msgstr "‘No we don’t, reverend.’"

msgctxt "mn14:18.11"
msgid "‘Kiṃ pana tumhe, āvuso nigaṇṭhā, jānātha—"
msgstr "‘But reverends, do you know"

msgctxt "mn14:18.12"
msgid ""
"ettakaṃ vā dukkhaṃ nijjiṇṇaṃ, ettakaṃ vā dukkhaṃ nijjīretabbaṃ, ettakamhi vā "
"dukkhe nijjiṇṇe sabbaṃ dukkhaṃ nijjiṇṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti?"
msgstr ""
"that so much suffering has already been worn away? Or that so much suffering "
"still remains to be worn away? Or that when so much suffering is worn away "
"all suffering will have been worn away?’"

msgctxt "mn14:18.13"
msgid "‘No hidaṃ, āvuso’."
msgstr "‘No we don’t, reverend.’"

msgctxt "mn14:18.14"
msgid "‘Kiṃ pana tumhe, āvuso nigaṇṭhā, jānātha—"
msgstr "‘But reverends, do you know"

msgctxt "mn14:18.15"
msgid ""
"diṭṭheva dhamme akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānaṃ, kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"upasampadan’ti?"
msgstr ""
"about giving up unskillful qualities in the present life and gaining "
"skillful qualities?’"

msgctxt "mn14:18.16"
msgid "‘No hidaṃ, āvuso’."
msgstr "‘No we don’t, reverend.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya19"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.94"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:19.1"
msgid "‘Iti kira tumhe, āvuso nigaṇṭhā, na jānātha—"
msgstr "‘So it seems that you don’t know any of these things."

msgctxt "mn14:19.2"
msgid "ahuvamheva mayaṃ pubbe na nāhuvamhāti, na jānātha—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn14:19.3"
msgid "akaramheva mayaṃ pubbe pāpakammaṃ na nākaramhāti, na jānātha—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn14:19.4"
msgid "evarūpaṃ vā evarūpaṃ vā pāpakammaṃ akaramhāti, na jānātha—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn14:19.5"
msgid ""
"ettakaṃ vā dukkhaṃ nijjiṇṇaṃ, ettakaṃ vā dukkhaṃ nijjīretabbaṃ, ettakamhi vā "
"dukkhe nijjiṇṇe sabbaṃ dukkhaṃ nijjiṇṇaṃ bhavissatīti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn14:19.6"
msgid "Na jānātha—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn14:19.7"
msgid ""
"diṭṭheva dhamme akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānaṃ, kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"upasampadaṃ."
msgstr ""

# BB’s evil-doers for kururakammanta is inexact. I always coorus in the specific sense of sopmeone who follows a cruel livelihood. eg AN 4.198, AN 6.57
msgctxt "mn14:19.8"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ sante, āvuso nigaṇṭhā, ye loke luddā lohitapāṇino kurūrakammantā "
"manussesu paccājātā te nigaṇṭhesu pabbajantī’ti?"
msgstr ""
"That being so, when those in the world who are violent and bloody-handed and "
"make their living by cruelty are reborn among humans they go forth as Jain "
"ascetics.’"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya20"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:20.1"
msgid ""
"‘Na kho, āvuso gotama, sukhena sukhaṃ adhigantabbaṃ, dukkhena kho sukhaṃ "
"adhigantabbaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"‘Reverend Gotama, pleasure is not gained through pleasure; pleasure is "
"gained through pain."

msgctxt "mn14:20.2"
msgid ""
"sukhena cāvuso gotama, sukhaṃ adhigantabbaṃ abhavissa, rājā māgadho seniyo "
"bimbisāro sukhaṃ adhigaccheyya, rājā māgadho seniyo bimbisāro "
"sukhavihāritaro āyasmatā gotamenā’ti."
msgstr ""
"For if pleasure were to be gained through pleasure, King Seniya Bimbisāra of "
"Māgadha would gain pleasure, since he lives in greater pleasure than "
"Venerable Gotama.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:20.3"
msgid "‘Addhāyasmantehi nigaṇṭhehi sahasā appaṭisaṅkhā vācā bhāsitā:"
msgstr "‘Clearly the venerables have spoken rashly, without thinking."

msgctxt "mn14:20.4"
msgid ""
"“na kho, āvuso gotama, sukhena sukhaṃ adhigantabbaṃ, dukkhena kho sukhaṃ "
"adhigantabbaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn14:20.5"
msgid ""
"sukhena cāvuso gotama, sukhaṃ adhigantabbaṃ abhavissa, rājā māgadho seniyo "
"bimbisāro sukhaṃ adhigaccheyya, rājā māgadho seniyo bimbisāro "
"sukhavihāritaro āyasmatā gotamenā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn14:20.6"
msgid "Api ca ahameva tattha paṭipucchitabbo:"
msgstr "Rather, I’m the one who should be asked about"

msgctxt "mn14:20.7"
msgid ""
"“ko nu kho āyasmantānaṃ sukhavihāritaro rājā vā māgadho seniyo bimbisāro "
"āyasmā vā gotamo”ti?"
msgstr "who lives in greater pleasure, King Bimbisāra or Venerable Gotama?’"

msgctxt "mn14:20.8"
msgid ""
"Addhāvuso gotama, amhehi sahasā appaṭisaṅkhā vācā bhāsitā, na kho, āvuso "
"gotama, sukhena sukhaṃ adhigantabbaṃ, dukkhena kho sukhaṃ adhigantabbaṃ;"
msgstr "‘Clearly we spoke rashly and without thinking."

msgctxt "mn14:20.9"
msgid ""
"sukhena cāvuso gotama, sukhaṃ adhigantabbaṃ abhavissa, rājā māgadho seniyo "
"bimbisāro sukhaṃ adhigaccheyya, rājā māgadho seniyo bimbisāro "
"sukhavihāritaro āyasmatā gotamenāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn14:20.10"
msgid "Api ca tiṭṭhatetaṃ, idānipi mayaṃ āyasmantaṃ gotamaṃ pucchāma:"
msgstr "But forget about that. Now we ask Venerable Gotama:"

msgctxt "mn14:20.11"
msgid ""
"“ko nu kho āyasmantānaṃ sukhavihāritaro rājā vā māgadho seniyo bimbisāro "
"āyasmā vā gotamo”ti?"
msgstr "\"Who lives in greater pleasure, King Bimbisāra or Venerable Gotama?\"'"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya21"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:21.1"
msgid ""
"Tena hāvuso nigaṇṭhā, tumheva tattha paṭipucchissāmi, yathā vo khameyya "
"tathā naṃ byākareyyātha."
msgstr ""
"‘Well then, reverends, I’ll ask you about this in return, and you can answer "
"as you like."

msgctxt "mn14:21.2"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññathāvuso nigaṇṭhā, pahoti rājā māgadho seniyo bimbisāro, "
msgstr "What do you think, reverends? "

msgctxt "mn14:21.3"
msgid ""
"aniñjamāno kāyena, abhāsamāno vācaṃ, satta rattindivāni ekantasukhaṃ "
"paṭisaṃvedī viharitun’ti?"
msgstr ""
"Is King Bimbisāra capable of experiencing perfect happiness for seven days "
"and nights without moving his body or speaking?’"

msgctxt "mn14:21.4"
msgid "‘No hidaṃ, āvuso’."
msgstr "‘No he is not, reverend.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:21.5"
msgid "‘Taṃ kiṃ maññathāvuso nigaṇṭhā, pahoti rājā māgadho seniyo bimbisāro, "
msgstr "‘What do you think, reverends? "

msgctxt "mn14:21.6"
msgid "aniñjamāno kāyena, abhāsamāno vācaṃ, cha rattindivāni … pe …"
msgstr ""
"Is King Bimbisāra capable of experiencing perfect happiness for six days …"

msgctxt "mn14:21.7"
msgid "pañca rattindivāni …"
msgstr "five days …"

msgctxt "mn14:21.8"
msgid "cattāri rattindivāni …"
msgstr "four days …"

msgctxt "mn14:21.9"
msgid "tīṇi rattindivāni …"
msgstr "three days …"

msgctxt "mn14:21.10"
msgid "dve rattindivāni …"
msgstr "two days …"

msgctxt "mn14:21.11"
msgid "ekaṃ rattindivaṃ ekantasukhaṃ paṭisaṃvedī viharitun’ti?"
msgstr "one day?’"

msgctxt "mn14:21.12"
msgid "‘No hidaṃ, āvuso’."
msgstr "‘No he is not, reverend.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.95"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:21.13"
msgid ""
"‘Ahaṃ kho, āvuso nigaṇṭhā, pahomi aniñjamāno kāyena, abhāsamāno vācaṃ, ekaṃ "
"rattindivaṃ ekantasukhaṃ paṭisaṃvedī viharituṃ."
msgstr ""
"‘But I am capable of experiencing perfect happiness for one day and night "
"without moving my body or speaking."

msgctxt "mn14:21.14"
msgid ""
"Ahaṃ kho, āvuso nigaṇṭhā, pahomi aniñjamāno kāyena, abhāsamāno vācaṃ, dve "
"rattindivāni …"
msgstr "I am capable of experiencing perfect happiness for two days …"

msgctxt "mn14:21.15"
msgid "tīṇi rattindivāni …"
msgstr "three days …"

msgctxt "mn14:21.16"
msgid "cattāri rattindivāni …"
msgstr "four days …"

msgctxt "mn14:21.17"
msgid "pañca rattindivāni …"
msgstr "five days …"

msgctxt "mn14:21.18"
msgid "cha rattindivāni …"
msgstr "six days …"

msgctxt "mn14:21.19"
msgid "satta rattindivāni ekantasukhaṃ paṭisaṃvedī viharituṃ."
msgstr "seven days."

msgctxt "mn14:21.20"
msgid ""
"Taṃ kiṃ maññathāvuso nigaṇṭhā, evaṃ sante ko sukhavihāritaro rājā vā māgadho "
"seniyo bimbisāro ahaṃ vā’ti?"
msgstr ""
"What do you think, reverends? This being so, who lives in greater pleasure, "
"King Bimbisāra or I?’"

msgctxt "mn14:21.21"
msgid ""
"‘Evaṃ sante āyasmāva gotamo sukhavihāritaro raññā māgadhena seniyena "
"bimbisārenā’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘This being so, Venerable Gotama lives in greater pleasure than King "
"Bimbisāra.’”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "mn14:21.22"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "mn14:21.23"
msgid "Attamano mahānāmo sakko bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti."
msgstr "Satisfied, Mahānāma the Sakyan was happy with what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn14:21.24"
msgid "Cūḷadukkhakkhandhasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
